text: Volkswagen Vento was a car made by Volkswagen from 1992 through 1998. It is the European version of the Third Generation Volkswagen Jetta. == Engines == === Petrol engines === * 1.6 55 kW (75 hp) and 74 kW (100 hp) * 1.8 55 kW (75 hp) and 66 kW (90 hp) * 2.0 85 kW (115 hp) * 2.8 VR6 128 kW (174 hp) === Diesel engines === * 1.9 D 47 kW (64 hp) * 1.9 SDI 47 kW (64 hp) * 1.9 TD 55 kW (75 hp) * 1.9 TDI 66 kW (90 hp) and 81 kW (110 hp) Vento Category:1990s automobiles
title: Volkswagen Vento
